        "text": "Exodus 30:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".; לשׁרתו, \"to serve Him,\" Jahve, - a general expression, including all the other services in the sanctuary, which were reserved for the priests; and בּשׁמו לברך, to bless in His name, i.e., to pronounce the blessing in the name of the Lord over the people, according to the command in ",
